data.title: Emily Mclaughlin - Newspaper Photograph Signed Circa 1971
data.meta_description: Emily Mclaughlin - Newspaper Photograph Signed Circa 1971  - Item 295335. The actress is shown in character as nurse Jesse Brewer from the television series General Hospital in this 2½x4 black and white newspaper photograph. Newspaper Photograph signed: 'Emily McLaughlin' in red felt tip, B/w 2½x4, affixed to a 6x4 card (2 surfaces). Shop for  Emily Mclaughlin related autographs, signed photographs, historical documents and manuscripts from the world's largest collection. Every purchase includes our industry recognized COA. Worldwide shipping available.
